      *                  * fica contabile                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-cod-cli-rag-000  thru vis-cod-cli-rag-999    .
       acc-cod-cli-430.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se cliente non esistente                    *
