      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se campo da accettare                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tip-ope        not  = 0301 and
                     w-tes-tip-ope        not  = 0302 and
                     w-tes-tip-ope        not  = 0303 and
                     w-tes-tip-ope        not  = 0304
