      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tip-rsd (1)    =    zero
                     move  01             to   w-tes-tip-rsd (1)      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Next Screen da campi precedenti          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "NXSC"
                     perform vis-tip-rsd-000
                                          thru vis-tip-rsd-999
                     go to acc-tip-rsd-400.
       acc-tip-rsd-100.
