                                              (w-bsu-num-ele)         .
           move      srt-tac-sdb          to   w-bsu-tac-sdb
                                              (w-bsu-num-ele)         .
           move      srt-tvl-sdb          to   w-bsu-tvl-sdb
                                              (w-bsu-num-ele)         .
           move      srt-dts-sdb          to   w-bsu-dts-sdb
                                              (w-bsu-num-ele)         .
