           move      rf-sdb-cab-app       to   w-rig-cab-app (1)      .
           move      rf-sdb-ccc-app       to   w-rig-ccc-app (1)      .
           move      rf-sdb-cod-cbp       to   w-rig-cod-cbp (1)      .
