      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           perform   pos-cnf-mod-m01-000  thru pos-cnf-mod-m01-999    .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Riciclo                             *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           go to     pos-cnf-mod-520.
