      *                              * porto scadenza : riciclo a leg- *
      *                              * gere riga successiva            *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-imp-ris (1)    =    w-rig-imp-sdb (1)
                     go to pos-cnf-mod-620.
           go to     pos-cnf-mod-630.
       pos-cnf-mod-630.
