      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                =    e-not-err
                     go to pos-cnf-mod-640.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se scadenza non trovata             *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Emissione messaggio di errore   *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           perform   pos-cnf-mod-m21-000  thru pos-cnf-mod-m21-999    .
      *                              *---------------------------------*
