      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se scrittura testata movimento contabile    *
      *                  * non eseguita : a no aggiornamento           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cge-gep-ris-fst    =    spaces
                     go to cge-gep-ris-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     cge-gep-ris-999.
       cge-gep-ris-900.
      *              *=================================================*
      *              * Subroutine interna per scrittura testata movi-  *
      *              * mento contabile                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione work-area testata e prima   *
      *                  * riga movimento per aggiornamenti contabili  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "NO"                 to   l-cge-300-tip-ope      .
           perform   mdl-agg-cge-cll-000  thru mdl-agg-cge-cll-999    .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Preparazione link-area per testata          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Tipo operazione                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "WR"                 to   l-cge-300-tip-ope      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Data di registrazione                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-dat-reg        to   l-cge-300-dat-reg      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice causale contabile                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-top-cau-cge
                    (w-top-ele-inx)       to   l-cge-300-cod-cau      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Descrizione causale                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   l-cge-300-des-cau      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Si/No data scadenza                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "N"                  to   l-cge-300-snx-dts      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Data scadenza                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   l-cge-300-dat-sca      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Data documento                          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-ddo-rsd (1)    to   l-cge-300-dat-doc      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Numero documento                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-ndo-rsd (1)    to   l-cge-300-num-doc      .
       cge-gep-ris-909.
